  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and drain well.",
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lentils, vegetable broth, diced tomatoes, and dark brown sugar, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in the sliced hard-boiled eggs.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
